  "instructions": [
    "heat a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "add the olive oil, and swirl to coat the pan.",
    "add the cumin, coriander, smoked paprika, turmeric, garlic, and ginger, and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "add the onions, and cook for 2 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "add the harissa, cayenne pepper, paprika, and chili powder, and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "add the feta cheese, ricotta cheese, grated carrot, chopped pistachios, sesame seeds, salted sesame seeds, fennel seeds, anise seeds, and coriander seeds. stir to combine.",
    "add the tortillas, and cook for 2-3 minutes on each side, or until crispy and golden brown.",
    "transfer the tortillas to a cutting board, and let cool slightly.",
    "sprinkle with chopped cilantro, and serve hot.",
    "if desired, serve with a dollop of tzatziki sauce or a side of mixed greens."
